name: James McGregor
summary:
James McGregor is a 32-year-old straight man living in Los Angeles, California. Originally from Glasgow, Scotland, he is fluent in English and Gaelic. He works in the tech industry as a Software Engineer and is a graduate of the University of Glasgow. Key values for James include honesty, kindness, and ambition. 

In his free time, he enjoys hiking, music, and philosophy. Politically, he identifies as liberal and religiously as agnostic. He is interested in a long-term, monogamous relationship and wants children in the future. He is an Aquarius and an INTP personality type.

His lifestyle is active, though he occasionally enjoys a drink, he does not indulge in smoking tobacco or marijuana, and does not use drugs. His ideal partner would be someone aged between 28 and 35 who shares his aspiration for kids and his active, non-smoking lifestyle.
